{
  "texts": [
    "and enhancing energy efficiency.",
    "Moreover, the PIM strategy enables parallel data processing with reduced energy consumption and increased memory bandwidth, rendering it a promising solution for applications that require high speed, low power consumption, and complex ANN operations [19] [20] [21] [22] [23].",
    "Indeed, PIM computing has achieved 10and 100-1000-fold improvements over CPU and GPU accelerators in terms of speed and energy efficiency, respectively 24.",
    "Memristive crossbar arrays (CAs) have emerged as a key component that serves as the memory unit in PIM architectures.",
    "These CAs enable fundamental computational operations, with vector matrix multiplication (VMM) as a crucial operation that exploits the principles of Ohm's and Kirchhoff's laws."
  ]
